## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of the relationship between architecture and the environment. The data is limited to the perspectives and information provided by the selected sources, which may not reflect the full scope of current architectural practices globally. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of sustainable architecture means that newer developments may not be captured in this report.